data.chText: 鲱鱼（产于北大西洋，成大群游动，可食）
data.enText: a N Atlantic fish that swims in very large groups and is used for food

means: 鲱鱼(产于北大西洋，成大群游动，可食)

tr: commercially important food fish of northern waters of both Atlantic and Pacific
valuable flesh of fatty fish from shallow waters of northern Atlantic or Pacific

value.def: A herring is a long silver-coloured fish. Herring live in large groups in the sea.

posc.def: Herring is a piece of this fish eaten as food.

trans: 银鸥(产于北大西洋，体大，翼端为黑色)
